images.name: PARK RIDGE TOWER
images.content: We're actively involved in the Park Ridge Tower and 6 Townhouse Commercial project in Dubai, UAE. M/S. Emaar Properties PJSC is our esteemed client, with U+A Architects providing consultancy. The main contractor overseeing the project execution is Engineering Contracting Co. LLC.

images.name: GRAND BLEU TOWER
images.content: We're handling the Grand Blue Tower project in Marsa Dubai, UAE for M/S. Emaar Properties PJSC. Working alongside consultant M/s. Mirage Leisure and Development LLC, Engineering Contracting Company LLC is overseeing the execution.

images.name: PARK HORIZON
images.content: We're actively working on the Park Horizon project in Dubai Hills Estate, UAE, for M/S. Emaar Properties PJSC. Our collaboration includes M/s. Mirage Leisure and Development LLC as the consultant, with project execution overseen by M/s. Parkway International Contracting LLC.

images.name: ARABIAN RANCHES III
images.content: We're currently involved in the Arabian Ranches III project in Dubai, UAE, for M/S. Emaar Properties PJSC. The consulting services are provided by M/s. Mirage Leisure and Development LLC, with the main contractor being M/s. Parkway International Contracting LLC.
